External Libraries
==================

The ext directory should contain the following git repos (latest commits should
suffice unless where indicated):

cereal - https://github.com/USCiLab/cereal.git
imgui - https://github.com/ocornut/imgui.git
	Use Commit 6ded5230d043aa32c755e65c910c2af5002fb9f9 (tag v1.92.6)
imgui_spinner - https://github.com/cmdwtf/imgui_toggle.git
imgui_sugar - https://github.com/mnesarco/imgui_sugar.git
imgui_toggle - https://github.com/cmdwtf/imgui_toggle.git
	May need adjustments to support imgui version above
magic_enum - https://github.com/Neargye/magic_enum.git
simpleini - https://github.com/brofield/simpleini
sqlite_modern_cpp - https://github.com/SqliteModernCpp/sqlite_modern_cpp.git
stb - https://github.com/nothings/stb.git

Structure Notes
==================

The executable consists of:

sorcery_core
sorcery_engine
sorcery_frontend
sorcery_gui
sorcery_modules
sorcery_resources
sorcery_types
dear_imgui

which are linked into sorcery.

Post-build
==========

The build automatically creates and copies these directories and their contents:

cfg/
dat/
doc/
gfx/
sfx/
vfx/

Debugging
=========

Both CMake Tools Debug and standard VS Code Debug are supported.